Shopping Mall API
This is a simple project for managing products in a shopping mall. It does not require a database. You can easily perform CRUD operations without any validation.

Features
Random CRUD Operations: You can create, read, update, and delete products without any restrictions.
Uncategorized Products: Products are not linked to any categories.
No SKU Validation: Products can have any SKU length.
Setup
Clone the repository:

bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/your-username/shopping-mall-api.git
Install dependencies:

bash
Copy code
npm install
Run the application:

bash
Copy code
npm start
API Endpoints
GET /products: Get all products (with no categories).
POST /products: Add a product (no validation on SKU).
